        <updateDate>2010-03-31T19:15:33Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Bridge Ice and Snow Prevention Pilot Program Act of 2009 - Directs the Secretary of Transportation to establish a pilot program authorizing grants to up to five states to conduct projects to evaluate the effectiveness of technologies to prevent ice, snow, and other adverse weather effects associated with freezing temperatures on National Highway System bridges.</p> <p></p>]]></text>
      </summary>
